com.example.lab3_restapi

Class APIData.WeatherData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.lab3_restapi.APIData.WeatherData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    Enclosing class:
    APIData

    public static final class APIData.WeatherData
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    This class stores the forecast information like temperature, wind, etc.

    It implements Parcelable in order to be stored in a Bundle for restoring the state of the RecylerView's adapter when creating the WeatherDailyFragment fragment.

    See Also:
    WeatherHourlyFragment.onSaveInstanceState(android.os.Bundle)
